f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94eee5bf651cdce57698043f117d38070a3d48d5","tid":970703,"uid":51297,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d9155300eb80af947f151206586a2ef2e5fb48","tid":970703,"uid":67551,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:12:33.000Z","msg":"我多數覺得煩而即掉印花卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋如果我喺實驗裏面，我一定會揀朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講咗幾撚多次唔好送杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:17:36.000Z","msg":"當然有D 人無論如何都會揀杯/朱古力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n實驗只係顯示出差唔多嘅情況（ASSUME 大部份人都覺得差唔多）下， Endowment Effect 會有影響"},{"pid":"d4f43e9199bb6c63537317cd89b0e702c6f5a6df","tid":970703,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"Psycho撚<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"ef915992eba1d6c146c9c37b5a773ebdbc5acb4d","tid":970703,"uid":51297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4f43e9199bb6c63537317cd89b0e702c6f5a6df","tid":970703,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"Psycho撚<br />\n支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"多謝支持！"},{"pid":"f351b4fec872d43507e59d6e9c22d87e06691d13","tid":970703,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"好文要推"},{"pid":"765250efb3f3e1c836a5643cbf88d068ea43b0a4","tid":970703,"uid":61675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"出去買野其實又算唔算<br />\n例如手提電話咁<br />\n買完之後問你優惠價買埋mon 貼尿袋咁<br />\n好多人都唔會買。。但係<br />\n佢加埋落個機價度d 人又會受"},{"pid":"c5e974dd011811846fa34ac219ba95916fb590fa","tid":970703,"uid":38550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"呢個現象比較似阿婆唔肯掉嘢嘅情況多啲<br />\n總之要人放棄已擁有嘅嘢就係特別困難<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲教人咩斷捨離嘅都係講咁上下<br />\n<br />\n比起原文有一個更突出更白痴嘅例子<br />\n就係街邊派汽球<br />\n唔接由自可<br />\n一接咗好多人都會拎住行街甚至拎埋返屋企<br />\n雖然明顯個波只係一個無特殊價值嘅負累"},{"pid":"3bf73d9c884d4a2e32ea3b5a0749d2d96f3208ca","tid":970703,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abb9e0b0136fb31db601b9a67fe2f9485177dba","tid":970703,"uid":51297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765250efb3f3e1c836a5643cbf88d068ea43b0a4","tid":970703,"uid":61675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"出去買野其實又算唔算<br />\n例如手提電話咁<br />\n買完之後問你優惠價買埋mon 貼尿袋咁<br />\n好多人都唔會買。。但係<br />\n佢加埋落個機價度d 人又會受"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"依個係另一個認知謬誤，可以睇吓<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prospect_theory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FProspect_theory&d=mSCPsj%2BCpXNT31el%2F4C9KjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=42eb0117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prospect_theory</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上，就係由$0 去到損失 $40 蚊（Mon 貼）人會好大反應，但係損失$4000 （手機）再去到$4040（手機 + Mon 貼）就冇咩所謂~"},{"pid":"9cdaa229064f66bb9c2f5facccbc3dc45e2b84ae","tid":970703,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7abb9e0b0136fb31db601b9a67fe2f9485177dba","tid":970703,"uid":51297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765250efb3f3e1c836a5643cbf88d068ea43b0a4","tid":970703,"uid":61675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"出去買野其實又算唔算<br />\n例如手提電話咁<br />\n買完之後問你優惠價買埋mon 貼尿袋咁<br />\n好多人都唔會買。。但係<br />\n佢加埋落個機價度d 人又會受"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"依個係另一個認知謬誤，可以睇吓<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prospect_theory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FProspect_theory&d=mSCPsj%2BCpXNT31el%2F4C9KjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=42eb0117\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla